A mesmerizing hourglass reimagined as a sleek modern sculpture, with thousands of tiny luminescent blue pixels cascading downward instead of sand, each pixel catching light as it falls through the narrow glass waist. The hourglass sits on a polished obsidian surface, surrounded by soft bokeh lights in the background. The glass vessel has elegant curved lines with a metallic rose gold frame. Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, dreamy atmosphere, warm ambient lighting casting gentle shadows, magical realism aesthetic with subtle sparkles floating in the air around the falling pixels.
